    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1597980/extras/e30e66784c8a8d2eb0ac574d32464ba7.poster.avif?t=1770657417\" width=600 height=248 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1597980/extras/e30e66784c8a8d2eb0ac574d32464ba7.webm?t=1770657417\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1597980/extras/e30e66784c8a8d2eb0ac574d32464ba7.mp4?t=1770657417\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>City 20，一座秘密核城市，在一次放射性泄漏后被隔离，并被迫陷入饥荒，一款末日后沙盒生存游戏，你的每一个选择都会改变周围的世界。</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在这款<strong>开放世界生存体验</strong>中，你的每个决定都会被记住。<strong>派系</strong>各怀心机，人们争夺利益，而环境本身就是持续的威胁。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>为了生存，你愿意付出多大代价？</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>无论你是否行动，世界都会发展变化</strong>。NPC遵循<strong>日常作息</strong>，适应<strong>动态环境</strong>，并记住你对他们的态度。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你可以帮助、交易、偷窃或攻击，但每一个行为都会影响你在个人和派系中的<strong>声望</strong>。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1597980/extras/4c6b6ce483d3905259adbca84595a80e.poster.avif?t=1770657417\" width=600 height=248 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1597980/extras/4c6b6ce483d3905259adbca84595a80e.webm?t=1770657417\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1597980/extras/4c6b6ce483d3905259adbca84595a80e.mp4?t=1770657417\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在这款<strong>充满活力的开放世界模拟</strong>中，与<strong>有组织的派系</strong>合作或为敌。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>赢得信任</strong>以进入商店、资源和安全区……或者<strong>背叛他们</strong>，被追捕、流放，并被逐出他们的领地。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1597980/extras/3faeaa781d4cc0586cd1640b8fc87615.poster.avif?t=1770657417\" width=600 height=248 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1597980/extras/3faeaa781d4cc0586cd1640b8fc87615.webm?t=1770657417\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1597980/extras/3faeaa781d4cc0586cd1640b8fc87615.mp4?t=1770657417\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >每个NPC都有自己的生活：工作、休息、吃饭，并适应这座<strong>活着的城市</strong>。饥饿的守卫可能会用情报换取食物；被冒犯的市民可能会数天不与你说话。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >帮助他们、利用他们或忽视他们…并<strong>观察城市的反应</strong>。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1597980/extras/733026d820844d4cd0255840718156d6.poster.avif?t=1770657417\" width=600 height=256 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1597980/extras/733026d820844d4cd0255840718156d6.webm?t=1770657417\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1597980/extras/733026d820844d4cd0255840718156d6.mp4?t=1770657417\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >辐射并非唯一的威胁。在你抵达后不久，奇怪的幻影开始涌入这座城市破败的街道。面对这种新的恐怖，政治必须被搁置，每个人都必须尽自己的一份力量来生存。你会召集各方势力坚守防线，还是任由这座城市陷入未知？</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1597980/extras/d712fa76a49ff3b4e4797b0f6ea502cc.poster.avif?t=1770657417\" width=600 height=248 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1597980/extras/d712fa76a49ff3b4e4797b0f6ea502cc.webm?t=1770657417\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1597980/extras/d712fa76a49ff3b4e4797b0f6ea502cc.mp4?t=1770657417\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >寻找食物、制作生存工具、恢复供电并应对危险。种植蔬菜以烹饪营养丰富的食谱，狩猎和捕捉野生动物，或收集稀有材料与NPC交易。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在<strong>没有预设路线</strong>的情况下，每一次游戏体验都是独一无二的：派系兴衰起落，NPC生死更替，联盟关系不可预测地变化。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >抢先体验</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >City 20正在积极开发中：我们不断扩展内容、优化系统，并根据社区反馈添加新功能。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >立即将其添加到愿望单，关注迈向1.0的旅程……并参与塑造游戏。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
